sect1.title: External Interfaces
sect1.para: The external interface of BuiltInList can be found in EA in the following location: VW_ICAS1.Chorus.All_Cores.SoftwareDecomposition.ComplexDeviceDrivers.ECU_DIAG_Chorus.BuiltInListChorus.SW Architecture.Static
A part of the external interfaces used by Built In List is provided by the component "RTE Light" and includes generated interfaces which are based on the SST_BUILTINLIST files.

sect1.title: External Dependencies
sect1.para: The module has dependencies to the following modules.
